      <div class="text-left">
        <p class="text-m">
          <img class="img-m img-fluid img-right d-block d-lg-none" src="/images/review/img3.png" />
          The content seems fresh and relevant to the seasons and the events celebrated during the season. Is there any synergy between the design and the content? Since the background of the website is white, white color is graceful and easy to the eye. Most images are photoshopped with white background which help the item to blend in the background of the website. In general, the overall responsiveness is complementing the navigational flow helping users to find their way through in an efficient way.<br />
          <a href="#top">Go to Top</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
