          Field validations are checking the input pattern as the user types the input, so if the user didn’t type @ symbol while typing email address the validation will prompt the user about the issue even before the submit button is being clicked. Another nice feature is as you hover over the icon of the shopping cart the icon will change into a text saying “Cart.”<br />
          <a href="#top">Go to Top</a>
        </p>
